domain

Class Department

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Department

  • public class Department
extends java.lang.Object
    The Department class represents a Department that could include Employees.

    Usage example: 
     Department myDepartment = new DePartment("Advising");
    Since:
    Version 1.8
    Author:
    Christopher Hield
    See Also:
    Employee, SalesEmployee, Timecard
